asStackTrace

public StackTraceElement[] asStackTrace()
Build a stack trace for this path. This can be used in generating more meaningful exceptions while using Crawljax in conjunction with JUnit for example.

Returns:
a array of StackTraceElements denoting the steps taken by this path. The first element [0] denotes the last Eventable on this path while the last item denotes the first Eventable executed.
